facts_and_links: {'Trivia': ['James Bond the ornithologist appears in this documentary via archive footage and dramatic re-enactments played by actor Gregory Itzin. Previous filmed productions to feature James Bond the ornithologist as a character in a dramatic context and not via footage of the real person are rare. These include Goldeneye (1989) where he was played by Reg Gadney and A Caribbean Mystery (2013) where he was portrayed by Charlie Higson. In the Bond movie Die Another Day (2002), Pierce Brosnan as the fictional James Bond posed as an ornithologist.', 'https://www.imdb.com/title/tt2587214/trivia/?ref_=tt_dyk_trv'], 'Quotes': ['Self - Theatre Director: I do know that Daniel Craig is blond because everybody wants to tell me that!', 'https://www.imdb.com/title/tt2587214/quotes/?ref_=tt_dyk_qu'], 'Alternate versions': ['"Our Name Is Bond" is a 52 minute shortened television version of the 2022 feature documentary film "The Other Fellow".\nThe difference in running times is about 28 minutes - the same number of Bond movies that exist at the time of production i.e. counting the 25 official EON productions and the three other unofficial titles.', 'https://www.imdb.com/title/tt2587214/alternateversions/?tab=cz&ref_=tt_dyk_alt'], 'Connections': ['Edited into Our Name Is Bond (2024)', 'https://www.imdb.com/title/tt2587214/movieconnections/?ref_=tt_dyk_cnn']}
